Thank you so much Ms. Grimes for being the voice for my husband and I when we did not know where to go or to start in the accidental situation we were in. Ms. Grimes is one of the best attorneys I have ever encountered because she is very loving, she cares, and she’s willing to go the extra mile for you. We had no idea how this whole situation was going to turn out but thanks to Ms. Grimes we were able to get justice and I have been referring her to others every sense.
Thanks again for all your help;

Mr&Mrs. Futrell
